trans-unit.source: Sorts a range by multiple keys. The call multiSort!("a.id < b.id", "a.date > b.date")(r) sorts the range r by id ascending, and sorts elements that have the same id by date descending. trans-unit.source: Struct for creating worker-local storage. Worker-local storage is thread-local storage that exists only for worker threads in a given TaskPool plus a single thread outside the pool. It is allocated on the garbage collected heap in a way that avoids false sharing, and doesn't necessarily have global scope within any thread. It can be accessed from any worker thread in the TaskPool that created it, and one thread outside this TaskPool. All threads outside the pool that created a given instance of worker-local storage share a single slot.
trans-unit.target: 用于创建工作人员本地存储的结构。本地工作存储是线程本地存储，仅对于给定 TaskPool 中的工作线程以及池外的单个线程存在。它以一种避免错误共享的方式分配到垃圾回收堆上，并且不必在任何线程内具有全局作用域。可以从创建它的 TaskPool 中的任何工作线程以及该TaskPool之外的一个线程中 TaskPool 。池外的所有创建工作人员本地存储实例的线程都共享一个插槽。
